# Logo Image Placeholder

Please replace this file with your actual BayT Designs logo image.

Expected format:
- File name: logo.png
- Recommended size: 48x48px (for navbar display)
- Format: PNG with transparent background
- The logo will be displayed in a 12x12 (48x48px) container

To update:
1. Delete this placeholder file
2. Add your actual logo.png file to this directory
3. The navbar will automatically display your logo

Current navbar logo settings:
- Container: w-12 h-12 (48x48px)
- Object fit: object-contain (maintains aspect ratio)
- Rounded corners: rounded-2xl
- Hover effects: scale-105 and shadow-xl
